# fa19-516-162: Cloudmesh Shell

## E.Cloudmesh.Shell.1: Install cmd5 and the command cms on your computer.

### Steps

1. Go to directory where virtual environment was created

    ``cd cm``
    
2. Activate virtual environment

    ``ENV3\Scripts\activate.bat``

3. Install the cloudmesh installer using pip

    ``pip install cloudmesh-installer``

4. Install cms using the cloudmesh-installer
    
    ``cloudmesh-installer git clone cms``
    
    ``cloudmesh-installer install cms -e``

5. Verify if cms is installed properly

    ``cms``

6. Exit the cms shell

    ``exit``
